{"id": 4175, "title": "Ticket #4175: Update Globus external to version 5.2.5", "description": "<blockquote>\nGlobus 5.2.1 is getting a little old, especially with recent changes to OpenSSL and 512-bit x509 keys now deemed too weak. We should update to the latest version.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Jan-23 16:48</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/a310bf694d79cd88895f4605a8cafa559075101c\">[39227]</a></span>: Update Globus external from 5.2.1 to 5.2.5. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4175\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4175'); return false;\" title=\"Update Globus external to version 5.2.5\">#4175</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Jan-23 16:48</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/ecdf609713cb9dcf1feb5fdb21e15ef94f40589b\">[39228]</a></span>: Remove most globus_libc_* calls in gahp_server. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4175\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4175'); return false;\" title=\"Update Globus external to version 5.2.5\">#4175</a></span> Most of the globus_libc_* calls now just call the underlying libc functions directly, with no added features. So let's just use the underlying libc functions.  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Jan-23 16:48</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/86de10820e03613d41a20232f6c2f782d09e8f54\">[39229]</a></span>: New Globus versions allow gt2 gahp to use authentication hack. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4175\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4175'); return false;\" title=\"Update Globus external to version 5.2.5\">#4175</a></span> We've confirmed that the gt2 gahp's hack to do parallel gsi authentications works with Globus versions up through 5.2.5.  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2014-Jan-27 13:45", "status": "resolved", "created": "2014-Jan-23 15:34", "fixed_version": "2014-Jan-23 15:34", "broken_version": "v080103", "priority": "3", "subsystem": "Libs", "assigned_to": "jfrey", "derived_from": "", "creator": "jfrey", "rust": "", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "", "due_date": ""}